Usage : grepTh string directoryName

After run this code , created  1 new file that is called as "log.txt".
The "log.txt" txt is result file.


when you run this code "make clean".  exe and .o files are cleaned.

***                                 ***                                             ***
***                                 ***                                             ***
	The file that is called "log.txt" is created as append mode in the code. Because of that the file is removed in the code with remove() function.
